      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. This unit has undergone a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service, ensuring structural integrity and mechanical longevity. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing the telepathic steering response these chassis are known for. Finished in a pristine Laguna Seca Blue, the paint depth and interior upholstery reflect a lifetime of climate-controlled storage and rigorous preventative maintenance.",
